# Group working state is runtime-generated and not version-controlled by default.
# Exception: `frontlane-lab-frontdesk` carries the Phase 0a prompt contract
# (V1 → MUAP migration artifact) and MUST be reviewable in git. See ADR-0008.
#
# Note 1: we use `groups/*` (not `groups/`) because git refuses to re-include
# any file whose parent directory was fully excluded with a trailing-slash
# pattern. With `groups/*`, the directory itself stays tracked-eligible, and
# `!groups/frontlane-lab-frontdesk` re-admits just that one subtree.
# Note 2: many users globally gitignore `**/CLAUDE.local.md` in
# `~/.config/git/ignore`. We override that here explicitly so the lab-frontdesk
# prompt contract is always tracked, regardless of user-level rules.
groups/*
!groups/frontlane-lab-frontdesk
!groups/frontlane-lab-frontdesk/CLAUDE.local.md
!groups/frontlane-lab-frontdesk/container.json
!groups/frontlane-lab-frontdesk/README.md

logs/

# .env.local.proposed is generated by `scripts/generate-env-local-proposed.ts`
# from the Phase 0 pack template. It is not a secret store — but it is also
# never the runtime config; users review it and choose what to merge into
# .env.local (which is already ignored above). See ADR-0008.
.env.local.proposed

container/agent-runner/node_modules/

*.sqlite
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.pid

# Agent working state (advisory, not authoritative — see CLAUDE.md §Session Continuation Guide)
.sisyphus/

